DISCLAIMER: Limited testing, not recommended for production use
without further testing - Use at own risk

Linux port of a FreeBSD utility to manage Boot Environments on ZFS
filesystems from here link

This script manages boot enviroment datasets and manipulates the
bootfs zfs property, so requires that the boot system read the
bootfs zfs property to decide on what dataset to boot.
